&hidm LSHFT 19               &hidm LSHFT 18 &hidm LSHFT 17 &hidm LSHFT 16 &hidm LSHFT 15 &hidm LSHFT 14                    &hidm RSHFT 14 &hidm RSHFT 15 &hidm RSHFT 16 &hidm RSHFT 17 &hidm RSHFT 18 &hidm RSHFT 19
